---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 356
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Act and Essence
By: St John of the Cross
---
A spark of pure love is more precious before God, more useful for the
soul and more rich in benedictions for the Church than all the other
works taken together, even if, according to appearances, one does
nothing.
